external_knowledge:
- The "most recent tournament" refers to the tournament with the latest start date;
- "stood tallest" is a metaphor for having the highest win percentages;
- "quintet" refers to the top 5 teams.

- "2023 tournaments" refers to tournaments that occurred in the year 2023;
- "best performance" is measured by the total number of wins and win percentage;
- "top 10" results are limited to the 10 teams with the highest wins and win percentages.

sql:
SELECT AVG(kills) AS average_kills
FROM player_tournament_stats
WHERE tournament_id = 1;

